text: Chhong Bunnath (born 28 November 1998) is a Cambodian footballer who plays for Angkor Tiger in the Cambodian League and the Cambodia U-23. ==Club career== Bunnath made his senior debut in Cambodia League in 2018 For Soltilo Angkor. ==International career== Bunnath made his senior debut in 2020 AFC U-23 Championship qualification against Australia national under-23 soccer team on 22 March 2019. ==External links== * Chhong Bunnath at NationalFootballTeams Category:Living people Category:Cambodia international footballers Category:1998 births Category:Cambodian footballers Category:People from Siem Reap Province Category:Association football central defenders
